{{Infobox football league season | country = {{ROU}} | competition = [[Liga IV]] | season = 2017–18 | prevseason = [[2016–17 Liga IV|2016–17]] | nextseason = [[2018–19 Liga IV|2018–19]] }}
The '''2017–18 Liga IV''' is the fourth level of the [[Romanian football league system]]. The champions of each county association play against one from a neighboring county in a playoff to gain promotion. From this season the counties were divided in 7 regions, each consisting of 6 counties and the draw was made on 28 February 2018, with 3 months and a half before the first matches.<ref>[http://www.prosport.ro/fotbal-intern/video-tragerea-la-sorti-a-barajului-pentru-liga-3-steaua-si-rapid-stiu-cu-cine-vor-juca-ce-adversari-vor-avea-fc-universitatea-craiova-as-brasov-si-ceahlaul-17036798 Tragerea la sorţi a barajului pentru Liga 3. Steaua şi Rapid ştiu cu cine vor juca! Ce adversari vor avea FC Universitatea Craiova, AS Braşov şi Ceahlăul]. prosport.ro {{ro}}</ref>
==2017–2018 Promotion Play-Off==
The matches are scheduled to be played on 16, 23 and 30 June 2018.<ref>[http://liga2.prosport.ro/liga-3/stiri/frf-stabileste-pe-28-februarie-meciurile-de-baraj-pentru-promovarea-in-liga-3-cele-sapte-regiuni-din-care-vor-fi-generate-21-de-jocuri-17024453 FRF stabileşte pe 28 februarie meciurile de baraj pentru promovarea în Liga 3. Cele şapte regiuni din care vor fi generate 21 de jocuri]. liga2.prosport.ro {{ro}}</ref>
