gion 4 (West)''' |colspan="2" style="background-color:#97DEFF"| {{OneLegResult| '''[[CS Hunedoara]]''' <small>([[Hunedoara County|HD]])</small> ||2-2| <small>([[Caraș-Severin County|CS]])</small> [[Voința Lupac]]}}||0-1||2-1 {{OneLegResult| '''[[CS Crișul Chișineu-Criș|Crișul Chișineu-Criș]]''' <small>([[Arad County|AR]])</small> ||7-0| <small>([[Gorj County|GJ]])</small> [[Petrolul Bustuchin]]}}||4-0||3-0 ([[Walkover|forfait]]) {{OneLegResult| '''[[ACS Dumbrăvița]]''' <small>([[Timiș County|TM]])</small> ||11-0| <small>([[Mehedinți County|MH]])</small> [[Viitorul Șimian]]}}||5-0||6-0 |- |colspan="3" style="background-color:#97DEFF"|'''Region 5 (South-West)''' |colspan="2" style="background-color:#97DEFF"| {{OneLegResult| '''[[ACS Flacăra Horezu|Flacăra Horezu]]''' <small>([[Vâlcea County|VL]])</small> ||9-0| <small>([[Teleorman County|TR]])</small> [[Rapid Buzescu]]}}||8-0||1-0 {{OneLegResult| '''[[Unirea Bascov]]''' <small>([[Argeș County|AG]])</small> ||3-1| <small>([[Olt County|OT]])</small> [[Vedița Colonești]]}} ||2-1||1-0 {{OneLegResult| [[Gloria Cornești]] <small>([[Dâmbovița County|DB]])</small> ||w/o| <small>([[Dolj County|DJ]])</small> '''[[FC U Craiova 1948|FC U Craiova]]'''}}||w/o||w/o |- |colspan="3" style="background-color:#97DEFF"|'''Region 6 (South)''' |colspan="2" style="background-color:#97DEFF"| {{OneLegResult| [[Abatorul Slobozia]] <small>([[Ialomița County|IL]])</small> ||3-5| <small>([[Ilfov County|IF]])</small> '''[[CSO Bragadiru]]'''}}||1-1||2-4 {{OneLegResult| [[FC Singureni]] <small>([[Giurgiu County|GR]])</small> ||1-17| <small>([[Bucharest|B]])</small> '''[[FC Rapid București|Rapid București]]'''}}||0-7||1-10 {{OneLegResult| '''[[Venus Independența]]''' <small>([[Călărași County|CL]])</small> ||6-2| <small>([[Prahova County|PH]])</small> [[CS Blejoi]]}}||5-1||1-1 |- |colspan="3" style="background-color:#97DEFF"|'''Region 7 (South-East)''' |colspan="2" style="background-color:#97DEFF"| {{OneLegResult| [[Sportul Ciorăști]] <small>([[Vrancea County|VN]])</small> ||2-5| <small>([[Constanța County|CT]])</small> '''[[CS Medgidia]]'''}}||2-2||0-3 {{OneLegResult| [[Pescărușul Sarichioi]] <small>([[Tulcea County|TL]])</small> ||1-8| <small>([[Buzău County|BZ]])</small> '''[[SCM Gloria Buzău|Gloria Buzău]]'''}}||0-3||1-5 {{OneLegResult| [[FC Universitatea Dunărea de Jos Galați|Universitatea Galați]] <small>([[Galați County|GL]])</small> ||4-7| <small>([[Brăila County|BR]])</small> '''[[CS Făurei]]'''}}||0-4||4-3 |}
