{{Infobox football club |clubname = AS Quatre Bornes |current = |image = AS_Quatre_Bornes_Logo.png |fullname = Association Sportive Quatre Bornes |nickname = |founded = |ground = [[Stade Sir Guy Rozemont]] |capacity = |owner = |chairman = |manager = |league = [[Mauritian League]] |season = | position = | pattern_la1 = | pattern_b1 = | pattern_ra1 = | pattern_sh1 = | pattern_so1 = | leftarm1 = | body1 = | rightarm1 = | shorts1 = | socks1 = | kit_alt1 = | pattern_la2 = | pattern_b2 = | pattern_ra2 = | pattern_sh2 = | pattern_so2 = | leftarm2 = | body2 = | rightarm2 = | shorts2 = | socks2 = | kit_alt2 = | pattern_la3 = | pattern_b3 = | pattern_ra3 = | pattern_sh3 = | pattern_so3 = | leftarm3 = | body3 = | rightarm3 = | shorts3 = | socks3 = | kit_alt3 = }}
'''Association Sportive Quatre Bornes''' is a [[Mauritius|Mauritian]] [[Association football|football]] club based in [[Quatre Bornes]], [[Plaines Wilhems District]]. In 2017-18, they play in [[Mauritian League]].<ref name="MFA">{{cite journal|url=http://www.mfa.mu/ |publisher=[[Mauritius Football Association]] |title=National Division 1 |accessdate=18 December 2012 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130417064734/http://www.mfa.mu/ |archivedate=17 April 2013 }}</ref>
==Ground== Their home stadium is [[Stade Sir Guy Rozemont]] in [[Quatre Bornes]].
==See also== * [[Mauritius Football Association]] * [[List of football clubs in Mauritius]]
