{{Infobox football league | name = MTN Elite two | logo = MTN_Elite_two.jpg | pixels = 200 | country = [[Cameroon]] | confed = [[Confederation of African Football|CAF]] | founded = | folded = | divisions = | teams = 14 | feeds = | promotion = [[MTN Elite One]] | relegation = | levels = | domest_cup = | confed_cup = | champions = | season = | most successful club = | tv = | website = | current = }}
The '''[[MTN Group|MTN]] Elite two''' (or ''Cameroon Deuxième Division'') is the second division of the Cameroon [[association football]] league system. It is organised by the [[Fédération Camerounaise de Football]]. Teams get promoted to the [[Elite One]].
