[[File:Front of the Guayama Convention Center.jpg|thumb|right|Guayama Convention Center, June 2011]]

'''Guayama Convention Center''' is a [[convention center]] in [[Guayama, Puerto Rico|Guayama]], [[Puerto Rico]]. It is one of the main performing arts and sports venues in Puerto Rico, especially in the south and southeast areas of the island.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mayaguez2010.com/es/instalaciones/deportivas/254-convenciones-guayama.html|title=Centro Convenciones Guayama|publisher=Comité Organizador de los XXI Juegos Centroamericanos y del Caribe Mayagüez 2010, Inc.| accessdate=5 Jul 2014}}</ref>

