The '''Havana Open''' was a [[golf]] tournament on the [[LPGA Tour]] from 1956 to 1958.<ref>[http://www.lpga.com/content/Chronology50-59.pdf LPGA Tournament Chronology 1950-1959]</ref> It was played at the Biltmore Country Club in [[Havana]], [[Cuba]].
